B%83n-h%E1%BB%93i-kha/poem-Y9KtIInHiAcU0MHtotu0zA">Tống đồng quận Bình Thuận đốc học La Đức Điển hồi kha - 送同郡平順督學羅德琠囬疴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/T%E1%BB%91ng-Trang-Xung-H%C6%B0-s%E1%BB%A9-Vi%E1%BB%87t/poem-SqnQBnzAIc-tyH8W1QcCCg">Tống Trang Xung Hư sứ Việt - 送莊沖虗使粵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-ZqGaWwKOrJXGaqhA3jlDaw">Viên Hoằng Đạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%E1%BB%A5/Tr%C3%ADch-L%C4%A9nh-Nam-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-t%C3%A1c/poem-00B55SYFOi2GLHTzo_vtog">Trích Lĩnh Nam đạo trung tác - 謫嶺南道中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%E1%BB%A5/author-rtTp4PUPw8zg7eBCEbPt6A">Lý Đức Dụ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/V%C5%A9-h%C3%A0nh/poem-mhqMJz3rm6EkpRr3HxYIjw">Vũ hành - 雨行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
